(2, 1, '2014-03-06 18:52:57', '2014-03-06 18:52:57', '<img class="aligncenter wp-image-3759" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/about-us1-300x170.png" alt="about-us1" width="150" height="85" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mapletree.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3886" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mapletree.png" alt="mapletree" width="300" height="354" /></a><span style="color: #580155;">Our story started with our love for everything maple and everything healthy. We are just a couple with a huge passion for all that is sweet, delicious, but most of all nourishing and beneficial for you. We are Matt and Andreea and we might just be the two biggest maple syrup enthusiasts on the planet! :)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #580155;">Our absolute fondness for maple soon attracted another advocate of this amazing sweet sap, our dear friend Randi, who joined us in our quest to share our love for maple with the world!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #580155;">Together, we form the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family!</span></p>\r\n[dt_sc_one_third first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Andreea" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/andreeapng.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Matt" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mattpng.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Randi" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Randipng.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #580155;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic gourmet maple treats! Our products are fully certified organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten-free, dye-free, soy free, and kosher.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3662" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/all3characters.png" alt="all3characters" width="200" height="175" /></p>\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/syrup.png" alt="placehold" />\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #580155;">The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our puff puffs, an amazing superfood that makes our puff puffs completely special and unique on the entire American market.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #580155;">We wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them. We replaced GMO with fully certified organic, we removed chemicals by opting for all natural and dye-free ingredients instead, but most of all, we made a point to replace processed refined sugars with the most delicious and wholesome raw sweetener known to man: maple syrup!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #580155;"><img class="alignright wp-image-3666" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/redmapleleaf.png" alt="redmapleleaf" width="200" height="213" /></span>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #580155;">We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #580155;">Our maple puff puffs are truly the next big thing, and we absolutely can not wait for the Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs to spread the love for maple with each and every one of you!</span></p>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2014-06-27 06:26:15', '2014-06-27 06:26:15', '', 0, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
