>Agriculture in Mesoamerica</a> and the Southeast and Southwest regions of the United States, the production of maple syrup is one of very few agricultural processes in the Northeast that did not come European colonists.\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_tab] [dt_sc_tab title="Is it healthy?" icon="fa-key"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span class="userContent">Maple Syrup contains iron, potassium, magnesium &amp; phosphorus - and has a higher calcium content that milk; it also contains small amounts of amino acids, proteins &amp; vitamins B2, B5 &amp; niacin</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span class="userContent"> Maple Syru<span class="text_exposed_show">p only has 40 calories per Tablespoon. Honey has 45, white sugar has 55 &amp; corn sugar has 60.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show"> Researchers have identified compounds in maple syrup with similar anti-inflammatory or anti-oxidant properties as blueberries, green tea and other superfoods</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show"> These compounds have been shown to fight cancer, diabetes and bacterial illnesses</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show"> Scientists have found that maple syrup''s natural phenols  potentially beneficial antioxidant compounds  inhibit two carbohydrate-hydrolyzing enzymes that are relevant to type 2 diabetes</span></span>[/dt_sc_tab]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[dt_sc_tab title="Why Organic?" icon="fa-thumbs-o-up"] [/dt_sc_tab] [dt_sc_tab title="Where can you find us?" icon="fa-plane"] We will be doing events all over Miami! Our event calendar lists where we will be and how you can find us. Please come try this amazing treat from the north that keeps you coming back for more![/dt_sc_tab] [/dt_sc_tabs_vertical] [dt_sc_hr_invisible] [dt_hr_title tag=''h2'']Our Gallery[/dt_hr_title] [dt_gallery_carousel limit=''8'' posts_design=''shape-one'' /] [dt_sc_hr_invisible] [dt_hr_title tag=''h2'']Recent Blog[/dt_hr_title] [dt_blog_posts posts_column=''one-half-column'' limit=''2'' excerpt_length=''20'' categories=''6''] [dt_sc_hr_invisible] [dt_hr_title tag=''h2'']Meet our Team[/dt_hr_title] [dt_sc_one_fourth first] [dt_sc_team name="Matthew Ondusko" image="http://placehold.it/460x460&amp;text=Team1" role="Co-Owner" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/] [/dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_team name="Ricky Semancik" image="http://placehold.it/460x460&amp;text=Team2" role="Co-Owner" skype="#" facebook="#" linkedin="#"/] [/dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_team name="Andreea Iosub" image="http://placehold.it/460x460&amp;text=Team3" role="Support" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/] [/dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_team name="Randi Shannon" image="http://placehold.it/460x460&amp;text=Team4" role="Franchise Manager" twitter="#" facebook="#" flickr="#"/] [/dt_sc_one_fourth] [dt_sc_hr_invisible]', 'Home Page II', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2992-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-12 02:47:07', '2014-03-12 02:47:07', '', 2992, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/2992-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
