(3415, 1, '2014-04-04 23:44:22', '2014-04-04 23:44:22', '[dt_facility_container title=''About Us'']\r\nOur story started with our love for everything maple! Four friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, and healthy; we are Matt, Randi, and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family.  \r\nFluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, all natural, pure Vermont maple syrup puff puffs.  The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our treats, an amazing "Superfood" that absolutely defines what the puff puffs are all about. \r\nWe wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them, by pumping each and every one of them with a full blast of maple flavor! We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything that we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well. \r\nBeing a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a Superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system. \r\nThis is why we do this! We want to glorify the all amazing maple in all of our puff puffs, and put a completely new healthy spin on cotton candy, popcorn, ice cream, and many many other old time favorites. \r\nOur maple puff puffs are the next big thing, and we are so excited to see everyone fall in love with everything maple as well!\r\n\r\n[dt_facility_item image=''http://wedesignthemes.com/themes/kidszone/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/baby1.png'' title=''In-house Design Classes''] <strong>Magni dolores</strong> eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur,