(3519, 1, '2014-04-25 21:44:29', '2014-04-25 21:44:29', 'Our Puff Puffs\r\nOrganic pure Vermont maple syrup is the hero in all of our delicious Puff Puffs! It is our main ingredient in all of our recipes, and we absolutely love it! Every Puff Puff is certified organic, all natural, vegan and gluten free, and we make a point to never use chemicals or dyes. Our mission is to put a healthy spin on all of your favorite treats, and serve them to you with so much love and joy!\r\n\r\nOrganic Maple Cotton Candy\r\nOur gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us! Its made with pure Vermont maple sugar, which is the crystalized form of maple syrup, and all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan and gluten free. We never add any dyes or anything artificial. Thanks to maple, this childhood favorite has become a guilt free treat that has you lick your fingers each time!\r\nOur flavors\r\n\r\nPure Maple\r\n<img src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/?attachment_id=3517" alt="Maple Syrup " />\r\nBlueberry Maple Pancake\r\n\r\nMaple Strawberry\r\n\r\nMaple Chocolate Fudge\r\n\r\nMaple Marshmallow\r\n\r\nMaple Dulce de Leche\r\n\r\nMaple Mango\r\n\r\nOrganic Maple Popcorn\r\nComing up soon!\r\n\r\nOrganic Maple Ice Cream\r\nComing up soon!', 'Our Puff Puffs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3421-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-25 21:44:29', '2014-04-25 21:44:29', '', 3421, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3421-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
