(3523, 1, '2014-04-25 22:04:32', '2014-04-25 22:04:32', '<h3>Our Puff Puffs Organic pure Vermont maple syrup is the hero in all of our delicious Puff Puffs! It is our main ingredient in all of our recipes, and we absolutely love it! Every Puff Puff is certified organic, all natural, vegan and gluten free, and we make a point to never use chemicals or dyes. Our mission is to put a healthy spin on all of your favorite treats, and serve them to you with so much love and joy!<!--more--></h3>\r\n<strong>Organic Maple Cotton Candy</strong>\r\nOur gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us! Its made with pure Vermont maple sugar, which is the crystalized form of maple syrup, and all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan and gluten free. We never add any dyes or anything artificial. Thanks to maple, this childhood favorite has become a guilt free treat that has you lick your fingers each time!\r\nOur flavors\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pure Maple</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Syrup1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3517" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Syrup1.jpg" alt="Maple Syrup" width="225" height="225" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Blueberry Maple Pancake</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Blueberry-Maple-Pancake.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3510" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Blueberry-Maple-Pancake-300x253.jpg" alt="Blueberry Maple Pancake" width="300" height="253" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Maple Strawberry</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Strawberry.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3515" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Strawberry.jpg" alt="Maple Strawberry" width="300" height="240" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Maple Chocolate Fudge</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Chocolate-Fudge.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3511" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Chocolate-Fudge-300x273.jpg" alt="Maple Chocolate Fudge" width="300" height="273" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Maple Marshmallow</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Marshmellow.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3514" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Marshmellow.jpg" alt="Maple Marshmellow" width="300" height="281" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Maple Dulce de Leche</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Dulce-De-Leche.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3512" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Dulce-De-Leche-300x203.jpg" alt="Maple Dulce De Leche" width="300" height="203" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Maple Mango</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Mango.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3513" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Maple-Mango-300x268.jpg" alt="Maple Mango" width="300" height="268" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Organic Maple Popcorn</strong>\r\n<em><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">Coming soon!</span></strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Organic Maple Ice Cream</strong>\r\n<em><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Coming soon!</strong></span></em>', 'Our Puf