lamcorper libero ipsum, id laoreet nisi mattis in. Suspendisse gravida dolor vitae iaculis sagittis. Vestibulum congue hendrerit massa, et rhoncus enim. Vestibulum congue hendrerit massa, et rhoncus enim. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Praesent ut vulputate purus, in ultricies massa. Curabitur vestibulum leo vel tortor iaculis tempor. Aenean varius leo in quam accumsan, convallis adipiscing orci tincidunt.\r\n[dt_facility_item image="#" title=''How we started''] <strong>Our story started with our love for everything maple! Four friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, and healthy; we are Matt, Randi, and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family.\r\nFluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, all natural, pure Vermont maple syrup puff puffs. The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our treats, an amazing "Superfood" that absolutely defines what the puff puffs are all about.\r\nWe wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them, by pumping each and every one of them with a full blast of maple flavor! We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything that we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.\r\nBeing a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a Superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.\r\nThis is why we do this! We want to glorify the all amazing maple in all of our puff puffs, and put a completely new healthy spin on cotton candy, popcorn, ice cream, and many many other old time favorites.\r\nOur maple puff puffs are the next big thing, and we are so excited to see everyone fall in love with everything maple as well!\r\n[/dt_facility_item]\r\n[dt_facility_item image=''#'' title=''Our Puff Puff Family''] <strong>Our Puff Puff family is always growing. We are working hard to introduce new healthy treats made from our organic maple! Currently we do Maple Cotton Candy and Vegan Maple Donuts! We are working towards new treats all the time, keep following us to discover our next big thing! [/dt_facility_item]\r\n[dt_facility_item image=''#'' title=''Our Vision for the Future''] </strong>Our hope is to bring our products all over and share these delicious healthy treats with all who enjoy good food. We love bringing smiles to everybody who gets a chance to try our amazing products and we hope to bring a smile your face at one of the next events we are at! [/dt_facility_item]\r\n[/dt_facility_container]</strong>\r\n\r\n[dt_intro_text type=''type3'']\r\n<h2>Becoming a Part of Our Team</h2>\r\n[dt_sc_four_fifth first]\r\n\r\nWe love sharing our products with everyone we meet, but we can only be so many places at once. Our hope is to share our products and our passion for quality with the world and help people start the home business they have always wanted. If you are interested in learning more click our button to the right!\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_four_fifth]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fifth]\r\n[dt_sc_button link="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/franchise-info/" size="medium" align="center" target="_blank"]Become a Franchise Owner[/dt_sc_button]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fifth]\r\n[/dt_intro_text]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_two_third first]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Meet our Team[/dt_hr_title]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Matthew Ondusko" image="http://placehold.it/460x460&amp;text=Team1" role="Co-Owner" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Andreea Iosub" image="ht