(3620, 1, '2014-05-22 12:45:33', '2014-05-22 12:45:33', '<strong>Thank you for your interest in Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs!</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are a growing successful mobile food franchisor whose mission is to offer a nutritious, healthy and delicious alternative to American favorite concessions, in the form of gourmet maple treats, made with organic pure maple syrup, and organic, all natural, dye-free, kosher, vegan and gluten free ingredients. Our franchisees recognize that the Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs concept is completely unique and answers a growing demand for amazing, tasty sweet treats that are also wholesome and nourishing.\r\n\r\nWe welcome enthusiastic entrepreneurs who can help us fulfill our maplelicious vision and want to join a successful venture that celebrates healthy in everything we do! If you are interested in becoming a Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs franchisee, we would love to hear from you.\r\n\r\nPlease contact Randi Shannon at (305)491-4597 for inquiries, or fill out the form below, and we will get in touch with you as soon as possible!\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id="3483" title="Untitled"]', 'Franchise inquiries', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3291-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 12:45:33', '2014-05-22 12:45:33', '', 3291, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3291-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
