(3632, 1, '2014-05-23 09:03:34', '2014-05-23 09:03:34', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Our Puff Puffs</h2>\r\n<span style="color: #f6550b;">Organic pure maple syrup is the hero in all of our delicious Puff Puffs! It is our main ingredient in all of our recipes, and we absolutely love it! Every Puff Puff is certified organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten free, kosher, and is completely free of all chemicals and dyes. Our mission is to put a healthy spin on all of your favorite treats, and serve them to you with so much love and joy!</span>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Organic Maple Cotton Candy [/dt_hr_title]\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;">Our gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us! Its made with pure maple sugar, which is the crystalized form of maple syrup, and all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan and gluten free. It is completely dye free and chemical free. Our beloved maple has transformed this childhood favorite into a guilt free treat that has you lick your fingers each time!</span>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Our Flavors[/dt_hr_title]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Pure Maple" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/pure-maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Blueberry Maple Pancake" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Blueberry-Maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Strawberry" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/strawberry.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Chocolate" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/coconut-chocolate.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Marshmallow" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/marshmellow.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Dulce de Leche" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/dulce-de-leche.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Mango" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mango.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n<center><strong>Organic Maple Popcorn</strong>\r\n<em><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">Coming soon!</span></strong></em></center><strong>Organic Maple Ice Cream</strong>\r\n<em><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Coming soon!</strong></span></em>', 'Our Puff Puffs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3421-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-23 09:03:34', '2014-05-23 09:03:34', '', 3421, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3421-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3633, 1, '2014-05-23 09:07:34', '2014-05-23 09:07:34', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Our Story!</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6eaf31;">Our story started with our love for everything maple and everything healthy! Three friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, nourishing and beneficial for you; we are Matt, Randi and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #eb5d0f;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten-free, kosher, pure maple syrup gourmet treats.</span>\r\n<span style="color: #a33072;"> The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our puff puffs, an amazing superfood that makes our puff puffs completely special and unique on the entire American market.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them. We replaced GMO with fully certified organic, we removed chemicals and dyes by opting for all natural and dye-free ingredients instead, but most of all, we made a point to replace processed refined sugars with the most delicious and wholesome raw sweetener known to man: maple syrup!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Being a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This is why we do this! We want to glorify the all amazing maple in all of our puff puffs, and put a completely new healthy spin on cotton candy, popcorn, ice cream, and many new treats we are working on.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Our maple puff puffs are truly the next big thing, and we are so excited to see everyone fall in love with everything maple as well!</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-23 09:07:34', '2014-05-23 09:07:34', '', 2, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3634, 1, '2014-05-23 09:08:34', '2014-05-23 09:08:34', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Our Story!</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6eaf31;">Our story started with our love for everything maple and everything healthy! Three friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, nourishing and beneficial for you; we are Matt, Randi and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #eb5d0f;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten-free, kosher, pure maple syrup gourmet treats.</span>\r\n<span style="color: #eb5d0f;"> The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our puff puffs, an amazing superfood that makes our puff puffs completely special and unique on the entire American market.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">We wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them. We replaced GMO with fully certified organic, we removed chemicals and dyes by opting for all natural and dye-free ingredients instead, but most of all, we made a point to replace processed refined sugars with the most delicious and wholesome raw sweetener known to man: maple syrup</span>!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Being a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This is why we do this! We want to glorify the all amazing maple in all of our puff puffs, and put a completely new healthy spin on cotton candy, popcorn, ice cream, and many new treats we are working on.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Our maple puff puffs are truly the next big thing, and we are so excited to see everyone fall in love with everything maple as well!</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-23 09:08:34', '2014-05-23 09:08:34', '', 2, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3635, 1, '2014-05-23 09:09:12', '2014-05-23 09:09:12', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Our Story!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6eaf31;">Our story started with our love for everything maple and everything healthy! Three friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, nourishing and beneficial for you; we are Matt, Randi and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #eb5d0f;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten-free, kosher, pure maple syrup gourmet treats.</span>\r\n<span style="color: #eb5d0f;"> The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our puff puffs, an amazing superfood that makes our puff puffs completely special and unique on the entire American market.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">We wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them. We replaced GMO with fully certified organic, we removed chemicals and dyes by opting for all natural and dye-free ingredients instead, but most of all, we made a point to replace processed refined sugars with the most delicious and wholesome raw sweetener known to man: maple syrup</span>!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Being a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.</p>\r\n<p style