(3674, 1, '2014-06-12 09:05:58', '2014-06-12 09:05:58', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Our Puff Puffs</h2>\r\n<span style="color: #f6550b;">Organic pure maple syrup is the hero in all of our delicious Puff Puffs! It is our main ingredient in all of our recipes, and we absolutely love it! Every Puff Puff is certified organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten free, kosher, and is completely free of all chemicals and dyes. Our mission is to put a healthy spin on all of your favorite treats, and serve them to you with so much love and joy!</span>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Organic Maple Cotton Candy [/dt_hr_title]\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;">Our gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us! Its made with pure maple sugar, which is the crystalized form of maple syrup, and all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan and gluten free. It is completely dye free and chemical free. Our beloved maple has transformed this childhood favorite into a guilt free treat that has you lick your fingers each time!</span>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Our Flavors[/dt_hr_title]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Pure Maple" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/pure-maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Blueberry Maple Pancake" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Blueberry-Maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Strawberry" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/strawberry.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Chocolate" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/coconut-chocolate.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Marshmallow" image="ht