(3695, 1, '2014-06-12 10:14:37', '2014-06-12 10:14:37', '<h2 class="titlebgr" style="text-align: center; line-height: 9;"><span style="color: #99cc00;">Organic Maple Cotton Candy!</span></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;"><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character.png"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character-191x300.png" alt="cotton-candy-character" width="191" height="300" /></a>Our gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us! \r\n\r\nIt might look like cotton candy, but it is not quite. There is not one granule of processed sugar of any kind in our maple cotton candy.  Its made from 100% pure organic maple sugar, nothing more and nothing less. Just the raw unprocessed wonderful maple goodness. All natural, completely non-allergenic, with absolutely no chemicals or artificial dyes. \r\n	\r\nThe process goes like this: maple tree - > maple sap - > maple syrup - > maple sugar - > Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs maple cotton candy!\r\n\r\nAs for our flavored maple cotton candy, all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan, gluten free, corn free and soy free. They all are completely dye free and chemical free as well. \r\n\r\nA delicious super healthy treat\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Our Flavors[/dt_hr_title]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Pure Maple" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/pure-maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Blueberry Maple Pancake" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Blueberry-Maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Strawberry" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/strawberry.png" /]\r\