(3737, 1, '2014-06-12 13:24:22', '2014-06-12 13:24:22', '<div class="titlebgr" style="height: 145px;"><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;padding-top: 45px;"><span style="color: #99cc00; line-height: 0">Organic Maple</span> <br> <span style="color: #99cc00; line-height: 0">Cotton Candy</span></h2></div>\r\n\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;"><span style="color: #a33070;">Our gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us! </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;">It might look like cotton candy, but it is not <a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character.png"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character-191x300.png" alt="cotton-candy-character" width="191" height="300" /></a>quite. There is not one granule of processed sugar of any kind in our maple cotton candy. Its made from 100% pure organic maple sugar, nothing more and nothing less. Just the raw unprocessed wonderful maple goodness. All natural, completely non-allergenic, with absolutely no chemicals or artificial dyes.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;">The process goes like this: maple tree - &gt; maple sap - &gt; maple syrup - &gt; maple sugar - &gt; Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs maple cotton candy!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;">As for our flavored maple cotton candy, all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan, gluten free, corn free and soy free. They all are completely dye free and chemical free as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33070;">A delicious super healthy treat</span>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Our Flavors[/dt_hr_title]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Cinnamon Maple" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/cinnamon-maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Chocolate" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/coconut-maple-chocolate.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Mango" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/coconut-maple-mango.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Dulce de Leche Maple" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/dulce-de-leche-maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Blueberry" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-blueberry.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Cofee" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-coffee.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Pumpkin Pie" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-pumpkin-pie.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Pure Maple Syrup" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Pure_Maple_Syrup.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Organic Maple Cotton Candy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3608-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 13:24:22', '2014-06-12 13:24:22', '', 3608, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3608-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
