(3763, 1, '2014-06-17 11:06:39', '2014-06-17 11:06:39', '<br><br><br><br><br><br><img class="size-medium wp-image-3759 aligncenter" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/about-us1-300x170.png" alt="about-us1" width="300" height="170" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Our story started with our love for everything maple and everything healthy! Three friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, nourishing and beneficial for you; we are Matt, Randi and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family!</span></p>\r\n[dt_sc_one_third first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Andreea" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/andreeapng.png" role="" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Matt" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mattpng.png" role="" skype="#" facebook="#" linkedin="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Randi" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Randipng.png" role="" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten-free, kosher, pure maple syrup gourmet treats.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/all3characters.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3662" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/all3characters.png" alt="all3characters" width="300" height="263" /></a></p>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/syrup.png" alt="placehold" />\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33072;">The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our puff puffs, an amazing superfood that makes our puff puffs completely special and unique on the entire American market.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33072;">We wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them. We replaced GMO with fully certified organic, we removed chemicals and dyes by opting for all natural and dye-free ingredients instead, but most of all, we made a point to replace processed refined sugars with the most delicious and wholesome raw sweetener known to man: maple syrup!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-medium wp-image-3666 alignright" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/redmapleleaf-281x300.png" alt="redmapleleaf" width="281" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Being a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">This is why we do this! We want to glorify the all amazing maple in all of our puff puffs, and put a completely new healthy spin on cotton candy, popcorn, ice cream, and many new treats we are working on.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Our maple puff puffs are truly the next big thing, and we are so excited to see everyone fall in love with everything maple as well!</span></p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-17 11:06:39', '2014-06-17 11:06:39', '', 2, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
