(3822, 1, '2014-06-17 15:14:39', '2014-06-17 15:14:39', '<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/why-maple-syrup.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3783 size-thumbnail" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/why-maple-syrup-150x100.png" alt="why-maple-syrup" width="150" height="100" /></a>\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_accordion_group]\r\n[dt_sc_toggle_framed title="Iron, Potassium, Magnesium &amp; Phosphorus"]Maple Syrup contains iron, potassium, magnesium &amp; phosphorus - and has a higher calcium content that milk; it also contains small amounts of amino acids, proteins &amp; vitamins B2, B5 &amp; niacin[/dt_sc_toggle_framed]\r\n[dt_sc_toggle_framed title="40 calories per Tablespoon"] Maple Syrup only has 40 calories per Tablespoon. Honey has 45, white sugar has 55 &amp; corn sugar has 60[/dt_sc_toggle_framed]\r\n[dt_sc_toggle_framed title="Anti-inflammatory or Anti-oxidant properties"]Researchers have identified compounds in maple syrup with similar anti-inflammatory or anti-oxidant properties as blueberries, green tea and broccoli; These compounds have been shown to fight cancer, diabetes and bacterial illnesses[/dt_sc_toggle_framed]\r\n[dt_sc_toggle_framed title="Carbohydrate-hydrolyzing enzymes"]Scientists have found that maple syrup''s natural phenols  potentially beneficial antioxidant compounds  inhibit two carbohydrate-hydrolyzing enzymes that are relevant to type 2 diabetes[/dt_sc_toggle_framed]\r\n[dt_sc_toggle_framed title="Easiest for our metabolism"]Maple syrup, compared to refined sugars, is the easiest for our metabolism to digest[/dt_sc_toggle_framed]\r\n[/dt_sc_accordion_group]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>The main nutritional value of maple syrup, per 100g is:</h2>\r\n[dt_sc_fancy_ul style="tick" variation="blue"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Calcium: 70 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Phosphorus: 8 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Potassium: 300 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Magnesium: 10 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Silica: 20 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Thiamine: 0.13 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Niacin: 0.10 mg</li>\r\n	<li>Riboflavin: 0.06 mg</li>\r\n	<li><span class="textexposedshow">Sodium: 10 mg</span></li>\r\n	<li><span class="textexposedshow">Iron: 1.20 mg</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/dt_sc_fancy_ul]', 'Why Maple Syrup? ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3578-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-17 15:14:39', '2014-06-17 15:14:39', '', 3578, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3578-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3823, 1, '2014-06-17 15:14:54', '2014-06-17 15:14:54', '<h2><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/why-organic.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3784 size-thumbnail" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/why-organic-150x100.png" alt="why-organic" width="150" height="100" /></a></h2>\r\n<h2>Producing organic maple syrup involves the respect of the environment, trees and the ecosystem of the maple bush through strict organic certification standards in processing the sap:</h2>\r\n[dt_sc_fancy_ul style="tick" variation="blue"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>No chemical fertilizers, pesticides or phytocides used in the maple bush or in the area w<span class="textexposedshow">here organic products are processed. If necessary, agricultural lime, wood ash or natural fertilizers may be used</span></li>\r\n	<li><span class="textexposedshow">A limit of three tapholes per tree. No over-tapping. No germicides (paraformaldehyde) in tapholes</span></li>\r\n	<li><span class="textexposedshow">Selective and correct use of vacuum tubing</span></li>\r\n	<li><span class="textexposedshow">Avoidance at all times of frequent use of machinery to prevent injury to the surfaced roots</span></li>\r\n	<li>No lead or lead solder used in the equipment required for processing organic maple products; consequently, there is no lead in the finished product. Lead can be a concern with some conventional maple syrup producers using older equipment</li>\r\n	<li>During the running season, the line system must be cleaned with natural biodegradable products</li>\r\n	<li>No synthetic chemical products used to control foam during boiling. Instead, a certified organic vegetable anti-foaming agent is used, such as safflower oil</li>\r\n	<li>The maple syrup is strained though a fine polyethylene membrane</li>\r\n	<li>Maple syrup is stores in stainless steel, instead of galvanized steel drums</li>\r\n	<li>Each bottle of organic maple syrup is traceable. Using the lot #, one is able to determine the manufacturer is, and when the syrup was produced</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/dt_sc_fancy_ul]', 'Why Organic?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3586-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-17 15:14:54', '2014-06-17 15:14:54', '', 3586, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3586-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3825, 1, '2014-06-19 09:25:38', '2014-06-19 09:25:38', '<img class="aligncenter wp-image-3759" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/about-us1-300x170.png" alt="about-us1" width="150" height="85" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Our story started with our love for everything maple and everything healthy! Three friends with a passion for everything sweet, delicious, nourishing and beneficial for you; we are Matt, Randi and Andreea, and we are the Fluffy Maple Puff Puff family!</span></p>\r\n[dt_sc_one_third first]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Andreea" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/andreeapng.png" role="" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Matt" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mattpng.png" role="" skype="#" facebook="#" linkedin="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_third]\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Randi" image="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Randipng.png" role="" twitter="#" skype="#" facebook="#"/]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_third]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs was born in March of 2014, and we sell organic, non-GMO, all natural, vegan, gluten-free, kosher, pure maple syrup gourmet treats.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3662" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/all3characters.png" alt="all3characters" width="200" height="175" /></p>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/syrup.png" alt="placehold" />\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33072;">The organic maple syrup is the superstar in all of our puff puffs, an amazing superfood that makes our puff puffs completely special and unique on the entire American market.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33072;">We wanted to take good old American favorite sweets and snacks, and completely reinvent them. We replaced GMO with fully certified organic, we removed chemicals and dyes by opting for all natural and dye-free ingredients instead, but most of all, we made a point to replace processed refined sugars with the most delicious and wholesome raw sweetener known to man: maple syrup!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">We celebrate maple and its mouth watering taste in every single one of our recipes, and we absolutely love that everything we offer is not only a source of delightful taste, but also an energizing, invigorating source of health as well.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-medium wp-image-3666 alignright" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/redmapleleaf-281x300.png" alt="redmapleleaf" width="281" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Being a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">This is why we do this! We want to glorify the all amazing maple in all of our puff puffs, and put a completely new healthy spin on cotton candy, popcorn, ice cream, and many new treats we are working on.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #a33072;">Our maple puff puffs are truly the next big thing, and we are so excited to see everyone fall in love with everything maple as well!</span></p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-19 09:25:38', '2014-06-19 09:25:38', '', 2, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
