(3898, 1, '2014-06-20 09:27:02', '2014-06-20 09:27:02', '<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/why-maple-syrup.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3783 size-thumbnail" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/why-maple-syrup-150x100.png" alt="why-maple-syrup" width="150" height="100" /></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3890" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png" alt="redleaf" width="25" height="27" /></a>\r\n\r\nRich in iron, potassium, magnesium &amp; phosphorus - and has a higher calcium content that milk\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3890" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png" alt="redleaf" width="25" height="27" /></a>\r\n\r\nContains small amounts<span class="apple-converted-space"></span><span class="textexposedshow">of amino acids, proteins, vitamins B2, B5 &amp; niacin</span>\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3890" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png" alt="redleaf" width="25" height="27" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span class="textexposedshow">Has only 40 calories per Tablespoon. Honey has 45, white sugar has 55 &amp; corn sugar has 60</span>\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3890" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png" alt="redleaf" width="25" height="27" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span class="textexposedshow">Has compounds with similar anti-inflammatory and anti-oxidant properties as blueberries, green tea, red wine and broccoli</span>; <span class="textexposedshow">these compounds have been shown to fight cancer, diabetes and bacterial illnesses</span>\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3890" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png" alt="redleaf" width="25" height="27" /></a>\r\n\r\nContains natural phenols, commonly found in berries, that have been found to inhibit two carbohydrate-hydrolyzing enzymes that are relevant to type 2 diabetes\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png"><img class="alignleft wp-image-3890" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/redleaf.png" alt="redleaf" width="25" height="27" /></a>\r\n\r\nIt is the easiest type of sugar for our metabolism to digest', 'Why Maple Syrup? ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3578-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-20 09:27:02', '2014-06-20 09:27:02', '', 3578, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3578-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
