gnleft wp-image-3900" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/orangeleaf.png" alt="" width="25" height="24" />It is the easiest type of sugar for our metabolism to digest\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/graph1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3901" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/graph1-300x186.png" alt="graph1" width="300" height="186" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/graph2.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3902" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/graph2-300x197.png" alt="graph2" width="300" height="197" /></a>', 'Why Maple Syrup? ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3578-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-20 09:51:22', '2014-06-20 09:51:22', '', 3578, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3578-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
