Organic Maple Ice Popcorn</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/ice-cream-60px.png"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/ice-cream-60px.png" alt="ice-cream-60px" width="39" height="60" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Organic Maple Ice Cream" href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/organic-maple-ice-cream/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #00ccff;">Organic Maple Ice Cream</span></a>', 'Our Puff Puffs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3421-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 06:36:19', '2014-06-27 06:36:19', '', 3421, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3421-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4106, 1, '2014-06-27 13:04:32', '2014-06-27 13:04:32', '<h2><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/organic-maple-cotton-candy.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3764 size-thumbnail" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/organic-maple-cotton-candy-150x89.png" alt="organic-maple-cotton-candy" width="150" height="89" /></a></h2>\n<span style="color: #000000;">Our gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us!</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">It might look like cotton candy, but it is actually quite different. As unbelievable as it might sound, this is actual healthy cotton candy!\n</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character.png"><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character-191x300.png" alt="cotton-candy-character" width="191" height="300" /></span></a></span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">There is not one granule of processed sugar of any kind in our maple cotton candy. Its made from 100% pure organic maple sugar, nothing more and nothing less. Just the unprocessed wonderful maple goodness. All natural, completely non-allergenic, with absolutely no chemicals or artificial dyes.</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">As for our flavored maple cotton candy, all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan, gluten free, corn free and soy free. They all are completely dye free and chemical free as well.</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">Being a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have scientifically acknowledged anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now officially acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">The process to make our maple cotton candy literally goes like this: maple tree  &gt; maple sap  &gt; maple syrup  &gt; maple sugar  &gt; Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs maple cotton candy!</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">It is without a doubt the healthiest and most delicious form of cotton candy in the world!</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">We are proud to say that we are the sole producers in the United States of 100% pure and organic maple syrup cotton candy, and the sole producers in the whole world of organic flavored maple syrup cotton candy!</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">An absolutely amazing treat that we hope you get a chance to fall in love with!</span>\n\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\n\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Our Flavors[/dt_hr_title]\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Pure Maple Syrup" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Pure_Maple_Syrup.png" /]\n\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Cinnamon Maple" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/cinnamon-maple.png" /]\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Chocolate" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/coconut-maple-chocolate.png" /]\n\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Mango" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/coconut-maple-mango.png" /]\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Dulce de Leche Maple" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/dulce-de-leche-maple.png" /]\n\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Blueberry" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-blueberry.png" /]\n\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Cofee" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-coffee.png" /]\n\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\n\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Pumpkin Pie" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-pumpkin-pie.png" /]\n\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]', 'Organic Maple Cotton Candy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3608-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 13:04:32', '2014-06-27 13:04:32', '', 3608, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3608-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4107, 1, '2014-06-27 06:41:14', '2014-06-27 06:41:14', '<h2><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/organic-maple-cotton-candy.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3764 size-thumbnail" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/organic-maple-cotton-candy-150x89.png" alt="organic-maple-cotton-candy" width="150" height="89" /></a></h2>\r\nOur gourmet maple cotton candy was the first Puff Puff in our family, and is a very dear one to us!\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">It might look like cotton candy, but it is actually quite different. As unbelievable as it might sound, this is actual healthy cotton candy!\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character.png"><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cotton-candy-character-191x300.png" alt="cotton-candy-character" width="191" height="300" /></span></a>\r\n\r\nThere is not one granule of processed sugar of any kind in our maple cotton candy. Its made from 100% pure organic maple sugar, nothing more and nothing less. Just the unprocessed wonderful maple goodness. All natural, completely non-allergenic, with absolutely no chemicals or artificial dyes.\r\n\r\nAs for our flavored maple cotton candy, all the flavors that we use are organic, natural, kosher, vegan, gluten free, corn free and soy free. They all are completely dye free and chemical free as well.\r\n\r\nBeing a natural unrefined sugar, with less calories than even honey, maple syrup is full of nutrients, minerals, and compounds that have scientifically acknowledged anti-oxidant, anti-inflammatory, anti-diabetes and anti-cancer properties. Maple syrup has now officially acquired the status of a superfood, and has joined the ranks of broccoli and berries in fighting for a stronger immune system.\r\n\r\nThe process to make our maple cotton candy literally goes like this: maple tree  &gt; maple sap  &gt; maple syrup  &gt; maple sugar  &gt; Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs maple cotton candy!\r\n\r\nIt is without a doubt the healthiest and most delicious form of cotton candy in the world!\r\n\r\nWe are proud to say that we are the sole producers in the United States of 100% pure and organic maple syrup cotton candy, and the sole producers in the whole world of organic flavored maple syrup cotton candy!\r\n\r\nAn absolutely amazing treat that we hope you get a chance to fall in love with!\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_hr_invisible]\r\n\r\n[dt_hr_title tag="h2"]Our Flavors[/dt_hr_title]\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Pure Maple Syrup" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Pure_Maple_Syrup.png" /]\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Cinnamon Maple" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/cinnamon-maple.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Chocolate" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/coconut-maple-chocolate.png" /]\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Coconut Maple Mango" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/coconut-maple-mango.png" /]\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth first]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Dulce de Leche Maple" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/dulce-de-leche-maple.png" /]\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Blueberry" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-blueberry.png" /]\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Cofee" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-coffee.png" /]\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[dt_sc_team name="Maple Pumpkin Pie" image="http://fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maple-pumpkin-pie.png" /]\r\n\r\n[/dt_sc_one_fourth]', 'Organic Maple Cotton Candy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3608-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 06:41:14', '2014-06-27 06:41:14', '', 3608, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3608-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
