(4110, 1, '2014-06-27 06:44:04', '2014-06-27 06:44:04', '<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/services.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3780 size-thumbnail" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/services-150x94.png" alt="services" width="150" height="94" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/all3characters.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3685" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/all3characters-300x263.png" alt="all3characters" width="200" height="175" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #470c0c;">Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs specializes in gourmet maple puff puffs, with a healthy twist: all organic, all natural, and free of all chemicals and dyes. Our company caters to events of all kinds, from birthday parties, to office events, to high end weddings. There is no occasion that our delicious puff puffs dont go well with!</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/cotton-candy60px.png"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/cotton-candy60px.png" alt="cotton-candy60px" width="38" height="60" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Organic Maple Cotton Candy Catering" href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/organic-maple-cotton-candy-catering/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">Organic Maple Cotton Candy</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/popcorn60px.png"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/popcorn60px.png" alt="popcorn60px" width="45" height="60" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Organic Maple Popcorn Catering" href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/organic-maple-popcorn-catering/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #99cc00;">Organic Maple Ice Popcorn</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/ice-cream-60px.png"><img class="alignleft size-full" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/ice-cream-60px.png" alt="ice-cream-60px" width="39" height="60" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Organic Maple Ice Cream Catering" href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/organic-maple-ice-cream-catering/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #00ccff;">Organic Maple Ice Cream</span></a>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3559-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 06:44:04', '2014-06-27 06:44:04', '', 3559, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3559-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4111, 1, '2014-06-27 06:45:28', '2014-06-27 06:45:28', '<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/omccc.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3881" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/omccc.png" alt="omccc" width="160" /></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandystick.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3936" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandystick.png" alt="cottoncandystick" width="200" height="192" /></a><span style="color: #8e0000;">Our elegant golden cotton candy is an absolute hit with all events, and is sure to make quite an impression! We can spin our cotton candy on site, or we can also prepackage it. We can customize our flavors for each event, and can also customize the cones, the packaging, and the labeling.<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandycone.png"><span style="color: #8e0000;"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-3935" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandycone.png" alt="cottoncandycone" width="150" height="359" /></span></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #8e0000;">The cotton candy servings can be as small or as large as you wish, and you can decide whether you wish for your event to offer limited or unlimited servings for your guests! We can even do fun things like serve the cotton candy on glow sticks, or straight on hard candy, or even serve the cotton candy in fun signature cocktails, or on top of desserts.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #8e0000;"></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #8e0000;">For weddings, we can serve the cotton candy canap style, on cute fancy trays in small individual servings, and for birthdays we can organize interactive spin it yourself cotton candy games! The sky is the limit when it comes to our maple cotton candy puff puffs! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #8e0000;"><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandycocktail.png"><span style="color: #8e0000;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3934" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandycocktail.png" alt="cottoncandycocktail" width="150" height="244" /></span></a>We love having fun with new ideas all the time, and always enjoy the challenge of customizing our cotton candy in a very unique way to suit you and your event!<a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandybag.png"><span style="color: #8e0000;"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-3933" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandybag.png" alt="cottoncandybag" width="200" height="196" /></span></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #a33072;"><span style="color: #8e0000;">The possibilities are truly endless! Please contact us for inquiries, and for a price estimate! Our catering specialists will be more than happy to work with you towards creating an impeccable and unforgettable Fluffy Maple Puff Puff experience at your event!</span><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3929" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cottoncandycanape.png" alt="cottoncandycanape" width="389" height="150" /></span>', 'Organic Maple Cotton Candy Catering', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3614-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 06:45:28', '2014-06-27 06:45:28', '', 3614, 'http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/uncategorized/3614-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
