(4114, 1, '2014-06-27 06:47:52', '2014-06-27 06:47:52', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/franchise2.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3970" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/franchise2.png" alt="franchise2" width="450" height="260" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #011917;"><strong>Thank you for your interest in Fluffy Maple Puff Puffs!</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #011917;">We are a growing successfulmobile food franchisorwhose mission is to offer a nutritious, healthy and delicious alternative to American favorite concessions, in the form of gourmet maple treats, made with organic pure maple syrup, and organic, all natural, dye-free, kosher, vegan and gluten<img class="alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-3940" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/greenleaf-150x150.png" alt="greenleaf" width="150" height="150" /> free ingredients. Our franchisees recognize that theFluffy Maple Puff Puffs concept is completely unique and answers a growing demand for amazing, tasty sweet treats that are also wholesome and nourishing.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #011917;">We welcome enthusiastic entrepreneurs who can help us fulfill our maplelicious vision and want to join a successful <a href="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mapleleaf.png"><span style="color: #011917;"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-3947" src="http://www.fluffymaplepuffpuffs.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/mapleleaf-150x150.png" alt="mapleleaf" width="150" height="150" /></span></a>venture that celebrates healthy in everything we do!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #011917;">If you are interested in becoming aFluffy Maple Puff Puffs franchisee, we would love to hear from you.</span></